  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为校准向导画一个流程图，核心是从初始页面到最终退出的完整状态流转。首先有个启动页叫\"Splash: Calibration Wizard\"，用户可以选择开始或取消。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S0",
        "EXIT_CANCEL",
        "N0"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，S0作为入口节点。那取消分支直接到EXIT_CANCEL，开始分支进入第一步。第一步是什么内容？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S0",
        "EXIT_CANCEL",
        "N0"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第一步是TRUE NORTH校准，标注为W000 000。这个页面需要支持三种操作：继续调整方位角、进入下一步，或者中断重启。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "N0",
        "S1",
        "S0"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，N0节点已添加，包含自循环的Move操作指向W000 000，Next箭头到S1，以及Stop+Restart返回S0。第二步呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "N0",
        "S1",
        "S0"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二步是DUE SOUTH，对应W180 000，交互逻辑和N0保持一致，也是三种操作。但这里有个细节——我写成\"W180 000\"的时候，你确认下格式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S0",
        "STAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "格式没问题，S1的自循环标注\"Move (W180 000)\"，Next到下一阶段。等等，你刚才说\"下一阶段\"，具体是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "STAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第三阶段叫Stage，让用户选择任意的park azimuth，标注为Wxxx 000，仰角固定EL=0。这个节点需要支持四种操作：调整方位角、返回上一步、中断重启，以及完成校准。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STAGE",
        "S1",
        "S0",
        "COMPLETE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "STAGE节点已添加，包含Move自循环、Back到S1、Stop+Restart到S0，以及Finish到COMPLETE。完成后的节点叫什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STAGE",
        "COMPLETE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "完成页叫\"Calibration Complete\"，从这里用户有三个选择：正常退出、重启整个向导，或者取消退出。正常退出需要带一个ok=True的标志。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPLETE",
        "EXIT_OK",
        "S0",
        "EXIT_CANCEL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，COMPLETE到EXIT_OK的边标注\"Continue\"，到S0是\"Restart Wizard\"，到EXIT_CANCEL是\"Cancel\"。EXIT_CANCEL是从S0和COMPLETE都能到达的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPLETE",
        "EXIT_OK",
        "S0",
        "EXIT_CANCEL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，EXIT_CANCEL是统一的取消出口，S0的Cancel和COMPLETE的Cancel都指向它。EXIT_OK只有COMPLETE能触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S0",
        "COMPLETE",
        "EXIT_CANCEL",
        "EXIT_OK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "所有节点和边已绘制完成。我检查一下：S0→N0是Start，S0→EXIT_CANCEL是Cancel；N0、S1、STAGE各自有Move自循环和Stop+Restart回S0；STAGE多了Back到S1。看起来完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S0",
        "N0",
        "S1",
        "STAGE",
        "COMPLETE",
        "EXIT_OK",
        "EXIT_CANCEL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，STAGE的Back箭头我刚才说错了——应该是回到S1，但S1是DUE SOUTH，逻辑上用户从STAGE返回应该到S1没错。不过我想确认下标注，是写\"Back\"还是\"Back ◀\"？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STAGE",
        "S1"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
