    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我目前标注的是\"Back\"，和Next的箭头方向对应。需要改成\"Back ◀\"来对称吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STAGE",
        "S1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "保持\"Back\"就行，简洁一些。另外我注意到N0和S1的Next标注，你用的是\"Next ▶\"，这个风格统一很好。STAGE的Finish也用\"Finish ▶\"保持一致。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "N0",
        "S1",
        "STAGE",
        "COMPLETE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，STAGE到COMPLETE的边现在标注\"Finish ▶\"。再核对一下方位角的表示：N0是W000 000，S1是W180 000，STAGE是Wxxx 000，EL=0。这些占位符格式正确吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "N0",
        "S1",
        "STAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "格式正确，Wxxx 000表示任意方位角，EL=0是固定仰角。还有个小问题——EXIT_OK和EXIT_CANCEL的节点描述，我原文是\"Exit wizard (ok = True)\"和\"Exit wizard (ok = False)\"，你那边显示正常吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EXIT_OK",
        "EXIT_CANCEL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "显示正常，两个退出节点都有明确的布尔标志。我注意到COMPLETE到EXIT_OK是Continue，到S0是Restart Wizard，到EXIT_CANCEL是Cancel。这里Restart Wizard和S0的Stop+Restart有什么区别？",
