      "utterance": "已按此风格统一：Move (W000 000)、Move (W180 000)、Move (Wxxx 000)都是带参数的，Next ▶和Finish ▶带方向箭头，Back、Stop + Restart、Continue、Cancel、Restart Wizard是纯文本。还有需要调整的吗？",
